Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.92,KagamiTsukasa,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs37.5\pos(161.3,290.6)}Trứng rán
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.92,KagamiTsukasa,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs37.5\pos(176.3,356.3)}Thịt xông khói
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.92,KagamiTsukasa,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs37.5\pos(183.8,498.8)}Hành và đậu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.92,KagamiTsukasa,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs37.5\pos(245.6,555)}Măng trộn
